ns and connection metadata while implementing the Bolt protocol API for Neo4j integrations.\",\nmetadata/org.neo4j.bolt/neo4j-bolt-connection-netty/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"Neo4j Bolt Connection Netty implements the Netty-based provider for Neo4j Bolt connections, including the bolt, bolt+s, and bolt+ssc schemes. It supplies asynchronous networking and protocol plumbing used by Neo4j drivers and related Neo4j integrations rather than a standalone end-user driver.\",\nmetadata/org.neo4j.bolt/neo4j-bolt-connection-netty/index.json:23:    \"description\" : \"Neo4j Bolt Connection Netty is the Netty-based reference implementation for creating Neo4j Bolt protocol connections from Java code. It provides asynchronous networking, message encoding, and protocol plumbing used by Neo4j drivers and related Neo4j solutions rather than a standalone end-user driver.\",\nmetadata/org.neo4j.bolt/neo4j-bolt-connection/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"Neo4j Bolt Connection provides Java APIs for creating and using Neo4j Bolt protocol connections. This artifact contains the provider SPI used by Neo4j drivers and related Neo4j solutions rather than an end-user driver.\",\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1782715690259}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_GcBuZfdVCvhXGIdhSWQiTPV2|fc_0e7090e5a7aa9979016a42152a09488197bc59ccde2aa1d5c6", "toolName": "bash", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "tests/src/org.neo4j.driver/neo4j-java-driver/5.28.5/src/test/java/org_neo4j_driver/neo4j_java_driver/ValuesTest.java\ntests/src/org.neo4j.driver/neo4j-java-driver/5.28.5/src/test/java/org_neo4j_driver/neo4j_java_driver/ListValueTest.java\ntests/src/org.neo4j.driver/neo4j-java-driver/5.28.5/src/test/java/org_neo4j_driver/neo4j_java_driver/ObjectInstantiatorTest.java\ntests/src/org.neo4j.driver/neo4j-java-driver/5.28.5/src/test/java/org_neo4j_driver/neo4j_java_driver/ConstructorFinderTest.java\ntests/src/org.neo4j.driver/neo4j-java-driver/5.28.5/src/test/java/org_neo4j_driver