 area if they remain sufficient.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Neo4j startup can be slow; tests need a bounded readiness loop rather than fixed sleeps.\",\n    \"Docker-backed tests must declare the required image and work with CI's pre-pulled/no-network isolation.\",\n    \"The current failing test is in value object mapping and may not require Docker to fix; use Docker only if expanding coverage to normal driver query execution.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e7090e5a7aa9979016a4215a97d0481979ad4f1b264178c48\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 5273, "output": 881, "cacheRead": 50688, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 56842, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782715805858, "responseId": "resp_0e7090e5a7aa9979016a42159f4da88197833f99110cfbe923"}}
